				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/Ch%C3%BAng-ti%C3%AAn-%C4%91%E1%BB%93ng-nh%E1%BA%ADt-v%E1%BB%8Bnh-ngh%C3%AA-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/poem-0wtH6a6e8ZaXuI5hUN4rRQ">Chúng tiên đồng nhật vịnh nghê thường - 眾仙同日詠霓裳</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/%C4%90%C3%A1p-H%E1%BB%93-Ch%C3%A2u-Ca-Di%E1%BB%87p-t%C6%B0-m%C3%A3-v%E1%BA%A5n-B%E1%BA%A1ch-th%E1%BB%8B-h%C3%A0-nh%C3%A2n/poem-XnuXHyis7SECQtus_88C3g">Đáp Hồ Châu Ca Diệp tư mã vấn Bạch thị hà nhân - 答湖州迦葉司馬問白是何人</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-Khanh/%C4%90i%E1%BB%81u-Kh%C3%AA-th%C3%B9-L%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-C%E1%BA%A3nh-bi%E1%BB%87t-h%E1%BA%ADu-ki%E1%BA%BFn-k%C3%BD/poem-Jn6RSrJuY7_bLD1ydYkECg">Điều Khê thù Lương Cảnh biệt hậu kiến ký - 苕溪酬梁耿別後見寄</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-Khanh/author-tOqeEdGQ0OZRwfU1Vi35GA">Lưu Trường Khanh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/%C4%90%E1%BB%91i-t%E1%BB%ADu-%E1%BB%A9c-H%E1%BA%A1-Gi%C3%A1m-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-6twF35-EeFmgVfiRu6Ia-w">Đối tửu ức Hạ Giám kỳ 1 - 對酒憶賀監其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%E1%BB%97/Ng%E1%BA%ABu-%C4%91%E1%BB%81/poem-A5xPZ8_roy4_TaiyZpnYQA">Ngẫu đề - 偶題</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%E1%BB%97/author-uSefdg6gWPnl7XHeM-UXCw">Trương Hỗ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/Th%C3%A1i-Th%E1%BA%A1ch-ho%C3%A0i-c%E1%BB%95/poem-7IG7eB_acAIsSZO-ZK5Yvg">Thái Thạch hoài cổ - 采石懷古</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%B